article_title: [爆卦] WHO宣布武漢肺炎為世界大流行
author: kobesuck5566 (摳比大懶趴)
content: Coronavirus confirmed as pandemic https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world51839944 WHO chief Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus said the number of cases outside China had increased 13fold over the past two weeks. He said he was deeply concerned by alarming levels of inaction over the vi rus. A pandemic is a disease that is spreading in multiple countries around the wor ld at the same time. However Dr Tedros said it was still not too late for governments to have an i mpact. All countries can change the course of this pandemic he said. Governments had to strike a fine balance between protecting health minimisin g disruption and respecting human life. This breaking news story is being updated and more details will be published s hortly. Please refresh the page for the fullest version. 世界衛生組織正在直播，譚德塞剛剛宣布武漢肺炎為世界大流行。 譚德塞指出，目前情況還不算太晚，各國政府應該做出相關決策來改變疫情的擴散。 直播連結： https://youtu.be/qgylp3Td1Bw 推 Golbeza : 真厲害 不愧是Winnie Happy Organization 61.231.85.138 03/12 00:42
